WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.230
Hey, good morning family. I have another

00:00:02.240 --> 00:00:04.630
video for you all today.

00:00:04.640 --> 00:00:06.789
The word that a lot of you all are

00:00:06.799 --> 00:00:10.150
getting at church is very lukewarm.

00:00:10.160 --> 00:00:12.230
They're not teaching you how to

00:00:12.240 --> 00:00:14.390
stand on your faith, how to believe by

00:00:14.400 --> 00:00:17.750
faith, or how to pray in the Holy Ghost.

00:00:17.760 --> 00:00:20.310
You would not believe the emails and the

00:00:20.320 --> 00:00:21.990
questions about the Holy

00:00:21.990 --> 00:00:22.000
Spirit—that

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:24.070
nobody knows how to pray in tongues.

00:00:24.080 --> 00:00:26.550
Nobody knows how to flow with the gifts

00:00:26.560 --> 00:00:30.070
and do what we are commissioned

00:00:30.080 --> 00:00:33.110
to do to be able to bring in the fire

00:00:33.120 --> 00:00:36.229
and get people free. A lot of people are

00:00:36.239 --> 00:00:38.630
so bound because of lack of knowledge.

00:00:38.640 --> 00:00:41.270
It says in the Bible, "My people perish

00:00:41.280 --> 00:00:43.990
for a lack of knowledge."I feel

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:46.069
like God has commissioned me and put

00:00:46.079 --> 00:00:48.389
me on this platform

00:00:48.399 --> 00:00:50.549
to tell you what the Holy Spirit has

00:00:50.559 --> 00:00:52.869
told me and all the knowledge that I've

00:00:52.879 --> 00:00:55.110
received over the years from some big

00:00:55.120 --> 00:00:57.430
ministries just dumping into me,

00:00:57.440 --> 00:00:59.750
continually feeding on

00:00:59.760 --> 00:01:03.430
the Word and

00:01:03.440 --> 00:01:06.070
staying on that potter's wheel, allowing

00:01:06.080 --> 00:01:09.510
the Holy Spirit to mold me. In that

00:01:09.520 --> 00:01:11.670
process, the potter's wheel has

00:01:11.680 --> 00:01:13.270
equipped me to be able to come on here

00:01:13.280 --> 00:01:15.750
today and be able to help you all. The

00:01:15.760 --> 00:01:18.230
Lord gave me

00:01:18.240 --> 00:01:21.910
a Ferrari to

00:01:21.910 --> 00:01:21.920
drive—this

00:01:21.920 --> 00:01:23.350
beautiful Ferrari because I love

00:01:23.360 --> 00:01:25.670
Ferraris and I think they're really

00:01:25.680 --> 00:01:28.710
amazing cars. So He gave me this

00:01:28.720 --> 00:01:30.070
amazing Ferrari. This is the way the

00:01:30.080 --> 00:01:31.510
Lord showed me in the spirit

00:01:31.520 --> 00:01:33.990
whenever I pray over it.

00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:36.950
I'm borrowing this Ferrari and

00:01:36.960 --> 00:01:39.830
driving it everywhere. I'm

00:01:39.840 --> 00:01:42.710
so excited to have this Ferrari, but Dad—my

00:01:42.710 --> 00:01:42.720
Father—let

00:01:42.720 --> 00:01:45.590
me borrow

00:01:45.590 --> 00:01:45.600
it.

00:01:45.600 --> 00:01:48.710
I don't have the title deed to

00:01:48.720 --> 00:01:51.270
the Ferrari by myself; they're not my

00:01:51.280 --> 00:01:53.270
keys. It's not anything;

00:01:53.280 --> 00:01:54.950
He's just allowing me to drive it, kind

00:01:54.960 --> 00:01:56.870
of like I would allow my son to drive my

00:01:56.880 --> 00:01:58.950
car. It's not his, but I'm allowing

00:01:58.960 --> 00:02:02.149
him to use it. So, I'm not in

00:02:02.159 --> 00:02:04.149
control of the Ferrari.

00:02:04.159 --> 00:02:06.149
I'm just allowed to drive

00:02:06.149 --> 00:02:06.159
it

00:02:06.159 --> 00:02:08.070
every once in a while when God says,

00:02:08.080 --> 00:02:11.110
"Hey, here's the keys. Drive

00:02:11.110 --> 00:02:11.120
it."Everybody's

00:02:11.120 --> 00:02:13.190
so excited and thinks you're

00:02:13.200 --> 00:02:16.309
so cool because of that Ferrari, but the

00:02:16.319 --> 00:02:19.430
Ferrari was never yours to begin with.

00:02:19.440 --> 00:02:21.030
And that's the way I look at the

00:02:21.040 --> 00:02:23.270
prophetic gifting.

00:02:23.280 --> 00:02:25.830
We have this treasure in earthen vessels

00:02:25.840 --> 00:02:28.390
that the excellency of the power will be

00:02:28.400 --> 00:02:31.430
known of Him and not of me.

00:02:31.440 --> 00:02:34.949
I don't control any of it. I

00:02:34.959 --> 00:02:36.869
can't make it happen. If I could,

00:02:36.879 --> 00:02:38.550
I would operate in it all the

00:02:38.560 --> 00:02:41.270
time.

00:02:41.280 --> 00:02:45.990
It comes by dying. You have to die to

00:02:46.000 --> 00:02:49.750
self. He

00:02:49.760 --> 00:02:52.869
entrusts you with more, and the more He

00:02:52.879 --> 00:02:55.270
entrusts you with, you're faithful

00:02:55.270 --> 00:02:55.280
with

00:02:55.280 --> 00:02:56.949
that amount of anointing. You're

00:02:56.959 --> 00:02:58.710
faithful with that part of the prophetic

00:02:58.720 --> 00:03:01.430
gift and He'll make you ruler over

00:03:01.440 --> 00:03:04.390
much. But if you're not faithful with

00:03:04.400 --> 00:03:08.070
the little and you don't handle this, He

00:03:08.080 --> 00:03:09.589
wants to see if it's going to destroy

00:03:09.599 --> 00:03:11.350
you. This is what He's wanting to see:

00:03:11.360 --> 00:03:15.350
Can your character

00:03:15.360 --> 00:03:19.750
handle this gift? If it can't, He

00:03:19.760 --> 00:03:22.710
doesn't say, "I'm done with you and I'm

00:03:22.720 --> 00:03:24.630
not going to use you

00:03:24.630 --> 00:03:24.640
anymore,"because

00:03:24.640 --> 00:03:26.550
the gifts and the callings of God are

00:03:26.560 --> 00:03:27.990
without repentance. They're on you

00:03:28.000 --> 00:03:30.949
regardless. But He wants to see

00:03:30.949 --> 00:03:30.959
if

00:03:30.959 --> 00:03:34.630
your character can handle that pressure

00:03:34.640 --> 00:03:37.350
of that gift, that Ferrari. Does the

00:03:37.360 --> 00:03:40.470
Ferrari change you, or do you

00:03:40.480 --> 00:03:42.390
just drive it and enjoy it

00:03:42.400 --> 00:03:44.229
until He says, "I need my keys

00:03:44.239 --> 00:03:47.270
back"?

00:03:47.280 --> 00:03:50.789
It's the same way. If you

00:03:50.799 --> 00:03:52.149
can't handle it, this is what He does:

00:03:52.159 --> 00:03:54.229
He puts you back on the potter's wheel. He

00:03:54.239 --> 00:03:55.750
puts you back on the potter's wheel and

00:03:55.760 --> 00:03:57.509
that water starts spinning

00:03:57.519 --> 00:03:59.110
around and around. You

00:03:59.110 --> 00:03:59.120
go

00:03:59.120 --> 00:04:00.949
faster and faster. He dumps

00:04:00.959 --> 00:04:03.190
some more water on you

00:04:03.190 --> 00:04:03.200
and

00:04:03.200 --> 00:04:05.509
puts a little bit more pressure there. I

00:04:05.519 --> 00:04:07.830
have a man who emails

00:04:07.830 --> 00:04:07.840
me—I

00:04:07.840 --> 00:04:10.470
don't remember

00:04:10.480 --> 00:04:12.390
your name, sir, I'd have to ask my wife,

00:04:12.400 --> 00:04:14.789
she tells me the emails—but he's a

00:04:14.799 --> 00:04:17.590
master potter and he makes sculptures

00:04:17.600 --> 00:04:20.310
and pottery for people.

00:04:20.320 --> 00:04:21.909
He's brilliant; I've seen him do his

00:04:21.919 --> 00:04:24.550
work. As he does his work, he puts

00:04:24.560 --> 00:04:27.749
his finger and his pressure on that

00:04:27.759 --> 00:04:30.230
pot and it makes it into a

00:04:30.240 --> 00:04:33.189
beautiful vase. That's the way we

00:04:33.199 --> 00:04:36.390
are in the spirit realm, y'all. If we're

00:04:36.400 --> 00:04:39.110
not ready, the Lord just puts us back on

00:04:39.120 --> 00:04:41.510
the potter's wheel. And this is the way

00:04:41.520 --> 00:04:43.909
it is a lot of times. I believe when you

00:04:43.919 --> 00:04:46.469
see people in the Bible,

00:04:46.479 --> 00:04:50.070
Moses took 80 years on the potter's

00:04:50.070 --> 00:04:50.080
wheel

00:04:50.080 --> 00:04:52.950
before he was used by God to go and lead

00:04:52.960 --> 00:04:56.230
the people out of Egypt. It took 80

00:04:56.240 --> 00:04:58.150
years for him to be on that potter's

00:04:58.150 --> 00:04:58.160
wheel

00:04:58.160 --> 00:05:00.230
for him to be ready. It

00:05:00.240 --> 00:05:03.270
took 80 years for him to die to self: 40

00:05:03.280 --> 00:05:05.510
years in the wilderness and 40 years being

00:05:05.520 --> 00:05:09.110
Pharaoh's son—80

00:05:09.110 --> 00:05:09.120
altogether.

00:05:09.120 --> 00:05:10.870
And then God said,

00:05:10.880 --> 00:05:13.510
"You're ready."He had a burning bush

00:05:13.520 --> 00:05:16.070
experience. In that experience of 80

00:05:16.080 --> 00:05:17.110
years, most people would have said,

00:05:17.120 --> 00:05:19.189
"Man, I'm 80 years old. My life's over.

00:05:19.199 --> 00:05:20.629
There's nothing that God can do with

00:05:20.629 --> 00:05:20.639
me."If

00:05:20.639 --> 00:05:23.029
you're 80 years old and

00:05:23.039 --> 00:05:24.790
you feel a tug on your heart to do

00:05:24.790 --> 00:05:24.800
something—maybe

00:05:24.800 --> 00:05:26.710
it's to make videos,

00:05:26.720 --> 00:05:28.469
maybe it's to do a YouTube channel,

00:05:28.479 --> 00:05:30.230
maybe God's called you to do something

00:05:30.230 --> 00:05:30.240
big—it

00:05:30.240 --> 00:05:33.029
is not over until

00:05:33.039 --> 00:05:35.670
it's over, as long as you stay on that

00:05:35.680 --> 00:05:38.230
potter's wheel.

00:05:38.240 --> 00:05:42.310
I feel the Holy Ghost,

00:05:42.320 --> 00:05:48.629
and when it comes on me, I start crying.

00:05:48.639 --> 00:05:50.469
As long as you stay on that potter's

00:05:50.479 --> 00:05:52.230
wheel,

00:05:59.919 --> 00:06:02.790
God's going to keep using you

00:06:02.800 --> 00:06:05.670
until the day He calls you home; there's

00:06:05.680 --> 00:06:08.070
nothing too big for God to work out in

00:06:08.080 --> 00:06:10.150
your flesh because the steps of the

00:06:10.160 --> 00:06:12.870
righteous are ordered of the Lord.

00:06:12.880 --> 00:06:14.950
What I'm trying to tell you is it

00:06:14.960 --> 00:06:16.550
took Paul and some of

00:06:16.560 --> 00:06:18.790
the disciples three years walking

00:06:18.800 --> 00:06:20.870
with Jesus before they started walking

00:06:20.880 --> 00:06:22.870
fully in their giftings and

00:06:22.880 --> 00:06:26.629
their call. But if you start saying, "I

00:06:26.639 --> 00:06:29.110
have this treasure in an earthen vessel

00:06:29.120 --> 00:06:31.270
that the excellency of the power may be

00:06:31.280 --> 00:06:35.189
known of Him and not of

00:06:35.199 --> 00:06:37.350
me,"He

00:06:37.360 --> 00:06:41.510
uses me; I don't use Him. Less of me,

00:06:41.520 --> 00:06:45.270
more of Him.

00:06:45.280 --> 00:06:48.390
In that process of being

00:06:48.390 --> 00:06:48.400
refined—the

00:06:48.400 --> 00:06:50.390
refiner's fire—what I'm trying to

00:06:50.400 --> 00:06:52.390
tell you all is what's coming to the body

00:06:52.400 --> 00:06:54.950
of Christ.

00:06:54.960 --> 00:06:57.350
There is a great revival that's about to

00:06:57.360 --> 00:07:00.950
take place—a massive outpouring. But I

00:07:00.960 --> 00:07:03.029
have told you what the Lord has showed

00:07:03.039 --> 00:07:05.830
me about a refiner's fire coming to His

00:07:05.840 --> 00:07:10.390
body. It is a massive move coming. Yes,

00:07:10.400 --> 00:07:13.589
it will be painful. A refiner's process

00:07:13.599 --> 00:07:16.629
is painful sometimes to the flesh. But

00:07:16.639 --> 00:07:19.749
in the process of the refiner's fire, it

00:07:19.759 --> 00:07:24.710
makes us less of us and more of Him.

00:07:24.720 --> 00:07:27.749
We have a treasure in an earthen vessel

00:07:27.759 --> 00:07:30.070
that the excellency of the power will be

00:07:30.080 --> 00:07:33.510
known of Him and not of us. Whenever we

00:07:33.520 --> 00:07:37.189
are dying to self—dying to our

00:07:37.189 --> 00:07:37.199
emotions—most

00:07:37.199 --> 00:07:39.589
people say, "Well, I've

00:07:39.599 --> 00:07:43.430
paid the price. I moved my family to

00:07:43.440 --> 00:07:47.990
wherever to go to Bible

00:07:47.990 --> 00:07:48.000
school."No.

00:07:48.000 --> 00:07:50.070
A person who's selling insurance will

00:07:50.080 --> 00:07:53.189
relocate and be a part of

00:07:53.199 --> 00:07:55.350
a new state or a new town. People are

00:07:55.360 --> 00:07:57.990
moving from California to go live by

00:07:58.000 --> 00:08:00.150
Elon Musk in his new factory. They're

00:08:00.160 --> 00:08:02.150
not going through a refiner's process

00:08:02.160 --> 00:08:04.550
because you moved your family. A

00:08:04.560 --> 00:08:07.270
refiner's process is to die

00:08:07.280 --> 00:08:09.909
to self. It's not my will,

00:08:09.919 --> 00:08:12.629
but Yours be done. When you get in that

00:08:12.639 --> 00:08:15.029
dying to self—not my will, but

00:08:15.039 --> 00:08:18.309
Yours be done every single

00:08:18.309 --> 00:08:18.319
day—that's

00:08:18.319 --> 00:08:20.629
what does it. The Apostle Paul says, "I

00:08:20.639 --> 00:08:24.469
die daily to myself that Christ may live

00:08:24.479 --> 00:08:27.189
in me."Christ needs to live in you. You

00:08:27.199 --> 00:08:29.270
need to be at that spout where the glory

00:08:29.280 --> 00:08:32.149
comes out. You need to be that person

00:08:32.149 --> 00:08:32.159
who

00:08:32.159 --> 00:08:34.709
is a yielded vessel that

00:08:34.719 --> 00:08:37.829
Jesus can use. Without being

00:08:37.839 --> 00:08:41.430
yielded and being dead to self,

00:08:41.440 --> 00:08:44.630
you'll never be

00:08:44.640 --> 00:08:47.030
that person that God can flow through to

00:08:47.040 --> 00:08:49.110
the point where blind eyes will

00:08:49.120 --> 00:08:52.389
open and deaf ears will pop open, the

00:08:52.399 --> 00:08:54.150
lame,

00:08:54.160 --> 00:08:59.110
the leper, the

00:08:59.110 --> 00:08:59.120
dead—all

00:08:59.120 --> 00:09:02.070
of it. Look at the process of even

00:09:02.080 --> 00:09:04.550
Jesus,

00:09:04.560 --> 00:09:06.949
the Son of God:

00:09:06.959 --> 00:09:11.190
33 years before He even died

00:09:11.200 --> 00:09:13.829
for us. But He was 30 years old before

00:09:13.839 --> 00:09:16.470
He even started His ministry.

00:09:17.920 --> 00:09:19.829
Jesus had to go through a refiner's

00:09:19.839 --> 00:09:23.269
potter's process,

00:09:23.279 --> 00:09:26.630
anointed to the full, had the

00:09:26.640 --> 00:09:28.870
Holy Spirit without measure,

00:09:28.870 --> 00:09:28.880
and

00:09:28.880 --> 00:09:31.750
went through a process of 30 years

00:09:31.760 --> 00:09:34.150
before He even said to Mary, "It's not

00:09:34.160 --> 00:09:37.110
my time."He even went through a process

00:09:37.120 --> 00:09:38.630
whenever He was turning the water into

00:09:38.640 --> 00:09:41.030
wine, His first miracle. Look at

00:09:41.040 --> 00:09:43.590
everything He went through; we don't have

00:09:43.600 --> 00:09:46.150
an account in the Gospels really of

00:09:46.160 --> 00:09:47.670
everything that He went through for

00:09:47.680 --> 00:09:49.990
those 30 years. But you know, it was

00:09:50.000 --> 00:09:53.430
something that he was in me, memorizing

00:09:53.440 --> 00:09:56.310
the Bible verses,

00:09:56.320 --> 00:09:58.630
the Torah,

00:09:58.640 --> 00:10:00.790
things like that, getting the word down

00:10:00.800 --> 00:10:04.470
inside of him. There was a

00:10:04.480 --> 00:10:05.910
process. That's what I'm trying to tell

00:10:05.920 --> 00:10:07.670
you all:

00:10:07.680 --> 00:10:10.550
we die daily. And that's why I was

00:10:10.560 --> 00:10:12.550
trying to tell this young man on

00:10:12.560 --> 00:10:15.350
Facebook

00:10:15.360 --> 00:10:17.990
that

00:10:18.000 --> 00:10:21.590
I have no ability on my

00:10:21.590 --> 00:10:21.600
own.

00:10:21.600 --> 00:10:24.389
I am nothing without the Holy

00:10:24.399 --> 00:10:27.670
Spirit telling me what to tell you all

00:10:27.680 --> 00:10:29.829
on this camera.

00:10:29.839 --> 00:10:33.269
I am so desperate as a man with hardly

00:10:33.279 --> 00:10:36.310
any education, with hardly anything to

00:10:36.320 --> 00:10:39.030
lean on in the natural for my

00:10:39.040 --> 00:10:41.509
flesh; he has stripped everything away

00:10:41.519 --> 00:10:45.509
from me. I feel like a skeleton a

00:10:45.519 --> 00:10:48.310
lot of times with the wind blowing.

00:10:48.320 --> 00:10:52.949
I'm so thirsty. I'm so hungry.

00:10:52.959 --> 00:10:55.750
And I have to sit at his feet for

00:10:55.760 --> 00:10:59.990
everything in my life: finances,

00:11:00.000 --> 00:11:03.269
stuff going on in my own flesh, my

00:11:03.279 --> 00:11:05.190
family, my children, my little girl who

00:11:05.190 --> 00:11:05.200
is

00:11:05.200 --> 00:11:07.190
overcoming.

00:11:07.200 --> 00:11:10.389
He keeps me in a place

00:11:10.399 --> 00:11:13.670
of desperation on him,

00:11:13.680 --> 00:11:16.949
stripping back all the flesh. Over the

00:11:16.959 --> 00:11:20.150
years, I've learned so much to

00:11:20.160 --> 00:11:22.710
lean on him,

00:11:22.720 --> 00:11:25.990
to seek him and I'll find him instead of

00:11:26.000 --> 00:11:28.470
trying to perform because of

00:11:28.480 --> 00:11:30.069
something I feel I have the

00:11:30.079 --> 00:11:33.110
ability to drive that Ferrari, and

00:11:33.120 --> 00:11:36.150
waiting on the Lord and being desperate

00:11:36.160 --> 00:11:39.590
in these end times.

00:11:39.600 --> 00:11:42.870
In the process of being desperate,

00:11:42.880 --> 00:11:45.509
I'll tell you a story. I put

00:11:45.519 --> 00:11:47.910
it on my Facebook trying to help people

00:11:47.920 --> 00:11:50.389
to tug them along the way. William

00:11:50.399 --> 00:11:52.949
Seymour in the Azusa Street

00:11:52.949 --> 00:11:52.959
Revival—he

00:11:52.959 --> 00:11:54.630
was blind in one eye. He was an

00:11:54.640 --> 00:11:57.030
African-American man. Prejudice was

00:11:57.040 --> 00:11:59.670
crazy back then. People were absolutely

00:11:59.680 --> 00:12:03.990
crazy over racial stuff, and

00:12:03.990 --> 00:12:04.000
he

00:12:04.000 --> 00:12:06.069
pressed through. He pressed through the

00:12:06.079 --> 00:12:08.949
refiner's fire. He pressed through the

00:12:08.959 --> 00:12:11.430
racial tension and all the stupidness of

00:12:11.440 --> 00:12:14.550
that. He pressed through it and

00:12:14.550 --> 00:12:14.560
refused

00:12:14.560 --> 00:12:18.629
to let the color of his skin, refused to

00:12:18.639 --> 00:12:21.670
let all the pressure from all of the

00:12:21.680 --> 00:12:25.670
drama from one eye or anything stop him

00:12:25.670 --> 00:12:25.680
from

00:12:25.680 --> 00:12:30.069
allowing himself to be used by God.

00:12:30.079 --> 00:12:33.190
It was a process.

00:12:33.200 --> 00:12:36.310
Here he was. Even whenever he started

00:12:36.310 --> 00:12:36.320
Azusa

00:12:36.320 --> 00:12:39.110
Street,

00:12:39.120 --> 00:12:41.269
he went in and started this

00:12:41.279 --> 00:12:45.670
in an old building.

00:12:45.680 --> 00:12:47.829
He would come down the stairs and put a

00:12:47.839 --> 00:12:51.350
box over his head and he would

00:12:51.360 --> 00:12:55.430
pray in that box until God would

00:12:55.440 --> 00:12:59.190
allow him to take it off and

00:12:59.200 --> 00:13:01.670
the glory would come in. This happened

00:13:01.680 --> 00:13:03.910
every single day for three and a half

00:13:03.920 --> 00:13:06.230
years, about the same time that Jesus was

00:13:06.240 --> 00:13:08.949
in his ministry.

00:13:08.949 --> 00:13:08.959
He

00:13:08.959 --> 00:13:12.069
walked in, and the power and the glory

00:13:12.069 --> 00:13:12.079
were

00:13:12.079 --> 00:13:14.629
so strong on him that his wife would

00:13:14.639 --> 00:13:16.389
have to sleep on the couch because the

00:13:16.399 --> 00:13:18.389
electricity, the power, and

00:13:18.399 --> 00:13:20.870
the Shekinah glory were so strong and

00:13:20.880 --> 00:13:23.990
manifested on him that it would

00:13:24.000 --> 00:13:27.509
even affect her sleep at night.

00:13:27.519 --> 00:13:29.430
If you touched him, the glory would flow

00:13:29.440 --> 00:13:31.670
out of him.

00:13:31.680 --> 00:13:34.310
But that came with a price, which is what I'm

00:13:34.320 --> 00:13:36.710
trying to tell you. It was a dying to

00:13:36.720 --> 00:13:39.269
self. Just like I'm trying to tell you

00:13:39.279 --> 00:13:41.829
what happens to me; it's a dying to

00:13:41.839 --> 00:13:44.629
self. Having a child with special needs,

00:13:44.639 --> 00:13:46.470
and the Lord tells you, 'Go and I

00:13:46.480 --> 00:13:47.990
want you to pray for people that are

00:13:48.000 --> 00:13:49.750
sick and I want you to lay hands on

00:13:49.750 --> 00:13:49.760
them.'And

00:13:49.760 --> 00:13:51.590
I say, 'Lord, I feel like a

00:13:51.590 --> 00:13:51.600
hypocrite.''Do

00:13:51.600 --> 00:13:54.550
it

00:13:54.550 --> 00:13:54.560
anyway.'And

00:13:54.560 --> 00:13:57.350
being obedient, God uses me and he

00:13:57.360 --> 00:13:59.590
touches people and they're healed. It's

00:13:59.600 --> 00:14:01.990
not me. If I

00:14:02.000 --> 00:14:04.470
could turn on that switch for myself,

00:14:04.480 --> 00:14:07.030
y'all, I would be able to

00:14:07.040 --> 00:14:08.870
pray for my little girl and see an

00:14:08.870 --> 00:14:08.880
instantaneous manifestation.

00:14:08.880 --> 00:14:11.189
I would go

00:14:11.199 --> 00:14:14.790
into these hospitals and

00:14:14.800 --> 00:14:17.189
pray for people and see them healed all

00:14:17.199 --> 00:14:20.470
the time. But the

00:14:20.480 --> 00:14:21.990
Lord turns the switch on, is what I'm

00:14:22.000 --> 00:14:24.069
trying to tell you. In the same way

00:14:24.079 --> 00:14:26.230
with William Seymour, he would sit there

00:14:26.240 --> 00:14:28.230
with that box on

00:14:28.240 --> 00:14:29.829
his head until the glory would settle

00:14:29.839 --> 00:14:32.550
in those meetings.

00:14:32.560 --> 00:14:34.150
And he would do that every single

00:14:34.160 --> 00:14:36.389
service. Sometimes it was five minutes,

00:14:36.399 --> 00:14:38.629
they say, and sometimes it was several

00:14:38.639 --> 00:14:40.230
hours, but he would just sit in there

00:14:40.240 --> 00:14:42.470
and they would sing songs. As crazy as

00:14:42.480 --> 00:14:44.949
that may sound, it's a humbling

00:14:44.959 --> 00:14:47.990
process. It's the Lord showing you:

00:14:48.000 --> 00:14:50.069
'This is not your Ferrari. You're just

00:14:50.079 --> 00:14:52.389
borrowing

00:14:52.389 --> 00:14:52.399
it.'And

00:14:52.399 --> 00:14:55.590
when you get a hold of that,

00:14:55.600 --> 00:14:58.310
God will start using you. It's not about

00:14:58.320 --> 00:15:01.110
you. Yes, you can walk around with the zeal

00:15:01.110 --> 00:15:01.120
of

00:15:01.120 --> 00:15:03.189
a teenager and be excited that God

00:15:03.199 --> 00:15:05.350
has a call on your life, and it's

00:15:05.360 --> 00:15:07.189
like he tips his hat to you. But he

00:15:07.199 --> 00:15:09.430
says, 'Get on the wheel. Get on the

00:15:09.440 --> 00:15:11.750
wheel and then I'll use you and I'll do

00:15:11.760 --> 00:15:13.829
something big in your life.'Without the

00:15:13.839 --> 00:15:16.389
potter's wheel

00:15:16.399 --> 00:15:19.110
and dying to self, self is in the

00:15:19.120 --> 00:15:21.430
way. Flesh is in the way. And you've got

00:15:21.440 --> 00:15:23.509
to get self and flesh out of the way.

00:15:23.519 --> 00:15:25.430
And the way you get it on there

00:15:25.440 --> 00:15:27.430
is by getting on your

00:15:27.440 --> 00:15:30.310
knees, praying in

00:15:30.320 --> 00:15:33.110
the spirit, refiner's fire, getting in

00:15:33.120 --> 00:15:36.710
the word, continually dying daily to

00:15:36.720 --> 00:15:38.230
self.

00:15:38.240 --> 00:15:43.430
And in that process,

00:15:43.440 --> 00:15:47.030
it would be all of him and none of you.

00:15:50.399 --> 00:15:52.389
I have this treasure in an

00:15:52.389 --> 00:15:52.399
earthen

00:15:52.399 --> 00:15:55.590
vessel, that the excellency of the power

00:15:55.600 --> 00:15:59.990
will be known of you, Lord, and not of me.

00:16:00.000 --> 00:16:02.870
I hope this message helped you today.

00:16:02.880 --> 00:16:05.990
This is what I had on my heart.

00:16:06.000 --> 00:16:08.230
Let me pray for you right now. Let me

00:16:08.240 --> 00:16:10.389
agree with you in prayer for some

00:16:10.399 --> 00:16:12.629
things you're believing for.

00:16:12.639 --> 00:16:15.590
Father, right now in the name of Jesus,

00:16:15.600 --> 00:16:18.470
we come before you boldly and we thank

00:16:18.480 --> 00:16:20.870
you, Father, that my brothers and

00:16:20.880 --> 00:16:23.749
sisters are hungry for you. There's

00:16:23.759 --> 00:16:25.990
a great revival that's about to take

00:16:26.000 --> 00:16:29.590
place upon this country.

00:16:29.600 --> 00:16:31.910
You've showed me this great revival even

00:16:31.920 --> 00:16:34.870
today. You told me about the tents. You

00:16:34.880 --> 00:16:37.590
told me about the people. You told me

00:16:37.600 --> 00:16:39.590
about the manifestations and the glory

00:16:39.600 --> 00:16:42.470
