00:16:42.480 --> 00:16:45.430
seen before. But I thank you, Father,

00:16:45.440 --> 00:16:49.350
for the refiner's fire. Make me better.

00:16:49.360 --> 00:16:52.949
Make me pure. By the fire that does

00:16:52.959 --> 00:16:55.910
refine where the breath of God is

00:16:55.920 --> 00:16:58.870
sweeter, there his brightest glory

00:16:58.880 --> 00:17:02.150
