00:17:02.160 --> 00:17:04.870
into fellowship with you. And in that

00:17:04.880 --> 00:17:07.270
light, I'll see the fountain of his

00:17:07.280 --> 00:17:11.029
blood that cleanses you. Father, I thank

00:17:11.039 --> 00:17:18.549
you for the refining fire today.

00:17:18.559 --> 00:17:21.990
Touch these people,

00:17:22.000 --> 00:17:23.829
