00:17:48.559 --> 00:17:52.950
We are stuck to you; we are

00:17:52.960 --> 00:17:55.669
stuck onto the

00:17:55.679 --> 00:17:58.390
main part of the vine. And I thank you,

00:17:58.400 --> 00:18:00.390
