00:19:51.120 --> 00:19:54.950
Help us to be more like you.

00:19:54.960 --> 00:19:59.590
Less of us and more of you.

00:19:59.600 --> 00:20:03.029
For in that, Father, is

00:20:03.039 --> 00:20:05.590
