00:20:08.240 --> 00:20:09.990
earth.

00:20:10.000 --> 00:20:12.390
Father, I thank you, Lord, that you create

00:20:12.390 --> 00:20:12.400
in

00:20:12.400 --> 00:20:15.430
us a clean heart. Create

00:20:15.430 --> 00:20:15.440
in

00:20:15.440 --> 00:20:18.870
